OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FITV News Tyne Tees Presenters Amy Lea
OL,7,Fand Ian Payne announce the search for
OL,8,Fhero fundraisers from North East and
OL,9,FNorth Yorkshire
OL,11,FNominations are now open as we look to
OL,12,Ffind a special fundraiser, or group of
OL,13,Ffundraisers, making a difference in
OL,14,Fthe North East and North Yorkshire,
OL,15,Ffor the Daily Mirror Pride of Britain
OL,16,FAwards.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/7
