OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FThere is no programme like it - first
OL,7,Ftelevised on ITV 26 years ago, it has
OL,8,Fcelebrated unsung heroes ever since -
OL,9,Fand we want to shine a light on those
OL,10,Fwho really deserve it.
OL,12,FIt is the night when so-called
OL,13,F"ordinary" people are thanked for
OL,14,Ftheir "extraordinary" contribution,
OL,15,Fowning the red carpet with an array of
OL,16,Fcelebrities who come to pay their own
OL,17,Ftributes.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
