OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F428A1781387268
OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FAmong them are fundraisers who don't
OL,7,Fseek the limelight - but are rightly
OL,8,Fgiven the credit they deserve on a
OL,9,Fnational stage.
OL,11,FNominations from across our region
OL,12,Fwill be narrowed down to a shortlist
OL,13,Fover the coming weeks, with one being
OL,14,Fnamed the ITV Tyne Tees Pride of
OL,15,FBritain Regional Fundraiser of the
OL,16,FYear.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
