OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FThey will then attend the national
OL,7,Fceremony in London alongside
OL,8,Ffundraisers from across the country,
OL,9,Fwith one of them taking home the
OL,10,Foverall nationwide award.
OL,12,FLast year's Tyne Tees winners were
OL,13,FNicola and Steven Wright from
OL,14,FMiddlesbrough, who have raised nearly
OL,15,F#40,000 for the Great North Air
OL,16,FAmbulance in memory of their 13-year-
OL,17,Fold son.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/7
