OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FCo-host Carol Vorderman has nothing
OL,7,Fbut admiration for the nominees,
OL,8,Fsaying, "It isn't necessarily about
OL,9,Fhow much money they've raised, but
OL,10,Fthey get out there and they do it, and
OL,11,Fdo it again, some over decades, some
OL,12,Ffor a particular project but the thing
OL,13,Fis it's never for them.
OL,15,F"We live in quite a greedy world and
OL,16,Fthere isn't a cell of greed inside
OL,17,Fthem and that inspires us to want them
OL,18,Fto do more."
OL,20,FHow to nominate
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
