OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FIf you know an individual or group
OL,7,Fwhose selfless fund-raising work has
OL,8,Fchanged lives for the better... now's
OL,9,Fthe time to let us know.
OL,11,FTo nominate, go to itv.com/
OL,12,Fprideofbritain
OL,14,FYou can nominate individuals or
OL,15,Fgroups, but only one person plus a
OL,16,Fguest can attend the Pride of Britain
OL,17,FAwards in London.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
