OL,3,CPride of Britain 2026: Search on for
OL,4,CITV Tyne Tees Fundraiser of the Year
OL,6,FNominees must be aged 18 or over and
OL,7,Fbe available to be filmed and have
OL,8,Ftheir fundraising story told on ITV
OL,9,FRegional News.
OL,11,FComplete the nomination form and tell
OL,12,Fus why your nominee(s) deserve this
OL,13,Faward. If you are under the age of 18
OL,14,Fplease get permission from a parent or
OL,15,Fguardian before you nominate.
OL,17,FNominations close Sunday 2 August 2026
OL,18,Fat 11.59pm.
OL,20,FFor T&Cs and Privacy Notice visit
OL,21,Fitv.com/terms
